34:59.366 --> 34:59.666
HEY.

34:59.733 --> 35:00.300
>> OH, GOSH.

35:00.366 --> 35:01.200
I THOUGHT IT WAS ONE OF THE

35:01.266 --> 35:02.000
QUEENS DRESSED UP AS A

35:02.066 --> 35:02.766
MARIONETTE DOLL.

35:02.833 --> 35:04.133
>> John: JUST ME IN MY ACTUAL

35:04.200 --> 35:04.766
HUMAN BODY.

35:04.833 --> 35:05.566
>> [LAUGHS]

35:05.633 --> 35:08.100
CUTE.

35:08.166 --> 35:11.966
[SNAPS]

35:12.033 --> 35:13.700
>> John: THAT WAS FUN.

35:13.766 --> 35:14.833
THAT WAS DEFINITELY FUN.

35:14.900 --> 35:15.466
NO POINT IN STOPPING IF WE GOT

35:15.533 --> 35:16.133
TIME.

