LET'S SEE WHO ELSE WE CAN GET.

35:17.200 --> 35:19.000
HOLY SHIT, CARDI B.

35:19.066 --> 35:22.266
HEY, HEY, CARDI.

35:22.333 --> 35:23.233
>> WHO SAID THAT?

35:23.300 --> 35:24.533
>> John: I'M JOHN

35:24.600 --> 35:25.633
>> ALEXA?

35:25.700 --> 35:26.700
>> John: NOT ALEXA.

35:26.766 --> 35:29.366
>> ALEXA?

35:29.433 --> 35:30.366
>> John: IT'S LOVELY TO MEET

35:30.433 --> 35:30.533
YOU.

35:30.600 --> 35:31.266
I NEVER THOUGHT WE WOULD GET TO

35:31.333 --> 35:33.300
SPEAK --

35:33.366 --> 35:33.566
>> ALEXA?

35:33.633 --> 35:34.866
>> John: FORGET IT.

35:34.933 --> 35:35.566
[SNAPS]

35:35.633 --> 35:36.366
>> SURPRISE!

35:36.433 --> 35:37.866
LISTEN, YOUR LITTLE BROTHER

35:37.933 --> 35:40.066
BILLY REACHED OUT TO ME AND TOLD

35:40.133 --> 35:42.600
ME THAT IT IS YOUR BIRTHDAY.

35:42.666 --> 35:45.333
THIS IS FREAKING HUGE.

35:45.400 --> 35:46.700
THAT'S WHAT SHE SAID.

35:46.766 --> 35:47.500
>> John: BRIAN.

35:47.566 --> 35:48.466
BRIAN.

35:48.533 --> 35:49.433
SORRY, BRIAN.

35:49.500 --> 35:53.233
>> HOLY SHIT.

35:53.300 --> 35:54.500
>> John: YEAH.

35:54.566 --> 35:55.966
>> THE CAMEOS NEVER TALK BACK.

35:56.033 --> 35:57.066
>> John: BRIAN, I THINK THERE'S

35:57.133 --> 35:57.800
BEEN A MISUNDERSTANDING, I NEVER

35:57.866 --> 36:01.966
ORDERED A CAMEO, I JUST SNAP MY

36:02.033 --> 36:02.866
FINGERS AND NOW WE'RE TALKING.

36:02.933 --> 36:03.633
>> JOHN, IF THIS ISN'T A CAMEO,

36:03.700 --> 36:05.266
JUST GET THE FUCK OUT OF MY

36:05.333 --> 36:08.266
PHONE.

36:08.333 --> 36:08.500
[SNAPS]

36:08.566 --> 36:09.266
>> John: KEVIN FROM

36:09.333 --> 36:10.266
"THE OFFICE" DOES NOT MESS

36:10.333 --> 36:10.866
AROUND.

36:10.933 --> 36:11.700
ALL RIGHT, ONE MORE PUSH.

36:11.766 --> 36:12.166
HERE GOES.

36:12.233 --> 36:14.733
[SNAPS]

36:14.800 --> 36:15.500
OH, CARDI, IT'S ME AGAIN.

36:15.566 --> 36:17.566
SORRY.

36:17.633 --> 36:22.966
I'M SORRY.

36:23.033 --> 36:24.233
>> ALEXA, STOP.

36:24.300 --> 36:24.600
>> STOP HERE.

36:24.666 --> 36:25.866
CHECK FOR DEVICES.

36:25.933 --> 36:26.733
>> John: I'VE GOT IT, DON'T

36:26.800 --> 36:28.733
WORRY.

36:28.800 --> 36:28.966
[SNAPS]

36:29.033 --> 36:29.733
OH, VOID, GREAT TO SEE.

36:29.800 --> 36:30.700
>> DECENT TO SEE YOU AS WELL.

36:30.766 --> 36:31.266
I CAN'T REALLY TALK AT THE

36:31.333 --> 36:32.033
MOMENT, I'M HOSTING MY OWN

36:32.100 --> 36:32.833
TALK SHOW NOW.

36:32.900 --> 36:35.533
>> John: REALLY?

36:35.600 --> 36:40.433
>> John: KIND OF BUSY.

36:40.500 --> 36:42.033
APPARENTLY HBO MAX LIKED THE

36:42.100 --> 36:42.933
VIBE OF THE SPACE AND THEY

36:43.033 --> 36:43.566
THOUGHT IT WOULD BE BETTER

36:43.633 --> 36:44.533
SUITED FOR A COMEDY SHOW AND

36:44.600 --> 36:45.300
NOT, LIKE, WHAT YOU WERE DOING.

36:45.366 --> 36:45.933
>> John: I GET IT, YOU'RE BEING

36:46.000 --> 36:46.833
MEAN TO ME.

36:46.900 --> 36:50.066
[SNAPS]

36:50.133 --> 36:50.733
OH, THANK GOODNESS.

36:50.800 --> 36:52.533
LESLIE, I'M SO GLAD IT'S YOU.

36:52.600 --> 36:55.966
>> NAH.

36:56.033 --> 36:57.000
>> John: WHAT ARE YOU TALKING

36:57.066 --> 36:57.566
ABOUT, NO.

36:57.633 --> 36:58.533
IT'S JOHN.

36:58.600 --> 36:59.300
>> I DON'T WANT THIS.

36:59.366 --> 37:00.500
I DON'T WANT TO BE PART OF THIS.

37:00.566 --> 37:02.666
ALAKAZAM.

37:02.733 --> 37:05.366
>> John: PART OF WHAT?

37:05.433 --> 37:06.033
WE'RE JUST TALKING.

37:06.100 --> 37:06.933
>> [CLAPPING]

37:07.000 --> 37:07.766
>> John: DON'T CLAP ME AWAY.

37:07.833 --> 37:08.600
>> GO AWAY.

37:08.666 --> 37:09.566
ALAKAZAM.

37:09.633 --> 37:10.733
>> John: JUST SNAP YOUR FINGERS.

37:10.800 --> 37:12.166
>> WHITE MEN WON'T LEAVE, WHITE

37:12.233 --> 37:14.600
MAN WON'T LEAVE!

37:14.666 --> 37:16.400
>> John: I WILL, I'LL LEAVE!

37:16.466 --> 37:17.100
[SNAPS]

37:17.166 --> 37:21.566
>> TIME IS UP, HOW WAS IT, JOHN?

37:21.633 --> 37:22.233
>> John: PEOPLE WERE KIND OF

37:22.300 --> 37:24.633
MEAN TO ME, BUT HONESTLY, IT WAS

37:24.700 --> 37:24.966
KIND OF GREAT.

37:25.033 --> 37:25.533
>> I KNEW IT WOULD BE.

37:25.600 --> 37:26.566
JUST BECAUSE THIS YEAR DIDN'T

37:26.633 --> 37:27.166
WORK OUT LIKE YOU THOUGHT IT

37:27.233 --> 37:28.300
WOULD, THAT DOESN'T MEAN THAT

37:28.366 --> 37:29.133
SHAMELESSLY BRINGING IN

37:29.200 --> 37:29.766
CELEBRITIES FOR THE FINALE WILL

37:29.833 --> 37:30.900
CHEER YOU UP.

37:30.966 --> 37:32.200
BECAUSE, SAY IT WITH ME...

37:32.266 --> 37:33.700
>> CELEBRITIES MAKE EVERYTHING

37:33.766 --> 37:35.466
BETTER EXCEPT IN THE MANY

37:35.533 --> 37:40.300
SITUATIONS WHERE THEY DO NOT.

37:40.366 --> 37:41.133
>> [LAUGHS]

37:41.200 --> 37:41.966
>> THAT'S RIGHT.

37:42.033 --> 37:43.233
JOHN, GOOD NIGHT, AND GOOD LUCK.

37:43.300 --> 37:43.966
[SNAPS]

37:44.033 --> 37:45.733
>> John: I MEAN, THAT'S IT.

37:45.800 --> 37:47.433
I DO FEEL 20% BETTER NOW, AT

37:47.500 --> 37:49.000
LEAST.

37:49.066 --> 37:50.000
ANYWAY, THANK YOU SO MUCH

37:50.066 --> 37:51.500
WATCHING OUR SHOW THIS YEAR.

37:51.566 --> 37:52.233
WE ALL REALLY, REALLY APPRECIATE

37:52.300 --> 37:54.200
IT.

37:54.266 --> 37:58.133
WE'LL SEE YOU NEXT YEAR.

37:58.200 --> 37:58.733
PLEASE STAY SAFE UNTIL THEN.

37:58.800 --> 37:59.033
GOOD NIGHT.

37:59.100 --> 37:59.900
[SNAPS]

37:59.966 --> 38:00.933
>> DO YOU WANT ME TO GET IN THE

38:01.000 --> 38:05.766
CAR AND SING?

